attributes.Title: On March 24th, 2022, Victoria Sergeyevna Rodina was sanctioned by the United States Treasury Department's Office of Foreign Assets Control (OFAC) pursuant to EO 14024 for "Blocking Property With Respect To Specified Harmful Foreign Activities of the Government of the Russian Federation" under RUSSIA-EO14024 sanction program and was added as Specially Designated Nationals (SDN).
On March 11th, 2022, Victoria Sergeyevna Rodina was sanctioned by the UK HMT pursuant to consolidated list of financial sanctions targets in the UK.

On February 25th, 2022, Victoria Sergeyevna Rodina was sanctioned by the Australian Government's Department of Foreign Affairs and Trade (DFAT) pursuant to Autonomous Sanctions (Designated Persons and Entities and Declared Persons—Ukraine) Amendment (No. 4) Instrument 2022.
